<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <title>Check your inbox — Whilly</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      max-width: 28rem; margin: 6rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    h1 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    p.muted { color: #6b7280; margin-top: 0; }
    .email-pill {
      display: inline-block; padding: 0.1rem 0.5rem; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      border-radius: 0.25rem; font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace;
    }
    .secondary {
      margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 0.9rem; color: #6b7280;
    }
    .secondary a { color: #2563eb; }
    .dev-note {
      margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.75rem; background: #fef3c7; border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
      border-radius: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #92400e;
    }
    .dev-note code { font-family: ui-monospace, monospace; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Check your inbox</h1>
  <p>
    We sent a sign-in link to <span class="email-pill">{{ email }}</span>.
    Click it to finish signing in. The link is valid for 15 minutes.
  </p>

  {# Dev-mode note — never renders the link itself. Operators retrieve the
     link from whilly_events.jsonl. Frontend F7 + Devil's Advocate #2. #}
  <div class="dev-note" role="note">
    Dev mode: the link was written to <code>whilly_logs/whilly_events.jsonl</code>
    (event type <code>auth.magic_link.issued</code>). Tail the file to copy the URL.
  </div>

  <div class="secondary">
    Wrong address? <a href="/login?email={{ email | urlencode }}">Send again</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
